        <h3 class="fw-bold">Craft Based Livelihood</h3>
        <p class="text-black">We are working for the upliftment of the artisans in the state of Chhattisgarh with the
          twin objectives of the revival of traditional handicrafts of Bastar and enhancing the incomes of the artisans
          while contributing towards establishing an exploitation-free society for the artisans. We have assisted
